notes: This is the 12th 50-run partnership between Hayden and Gilchrist in ODIs
When he reached 74, Gilchrist completed 1000 runs against India in ODIs
This is Gilchrist's highest ODI score against India. His previous best was 92 in Adelaide in 2000
This is Gilchrist's first ODI century against India. It came in his 25th ODI against India
The Australian score is the highest in an ODI at the M Chinnaswamy stadium. The previous best was 315 by India, against Austalia in 2001

milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (633) involving teams Australia & India in ODIs

stories.title: The silver lining for India
stories.subTitle: India v Australia, TVS Cup, Bangalore
stories.summary: Murali Kartik was the only Indian bowler who earned the respect of the Australian batsmen, especially Ricky Ponting

stories.title: Quixotic effort
stories.subTitle: India v Australia, TVS Cup, Bangalore
stories.summary: India's batsmen tilted bravely at windmills in the best traditions of Don Quixote, but ultimately, they were undone by a magnificent spell of bowling from one of Australia's forgotten men, and the ineptitude of their own bowlers earlier in the day
stories.byline: The Wisden Verdict by Dileep Premachandran

stories.title: Chaos theory
stories.subTitle: India v Australia, TVS Cup, Bangalore
stories.summary: The scene near Anil Kumble Circle half an hour before the game would have appealed to those addicted to chaos
